snippet.title: In Stars and Time - OUT NOW on PC, Switch, PS4, and PS5!
snippet.description:
In Stars and Time is OUT NOW on PC, Switch, PS4, and PS5!

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1677310/In_Stars_And_Time/
Nintendo Switch: https://www.nintendo.com/store/products/in-stars-and-time-switch/
PlayStation 4/5: https://store.playstation.com/concept/10007419

Live with the ever-present burden of being stuck in a time loop only you know about. Pray to the stars and free yourself from time. Find hope where there is none in this turn-based time-loop RPG adventure from developer insertdisc5.
